Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後我來守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖地跟著我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手嘛大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這就是告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡全力守護你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生帥爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺可靠的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個城市叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐斯提亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座城市裡我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級四班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關在了裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說世界只是個很小的共同體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要通破壞世界而去拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫助我拯救世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那就是拯救世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前要尋找一個叫疤面的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題反正我也不急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好318度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西北偏北3度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是一點誤差都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生請一直往前開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開吧開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoho　飆起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的巫拉殿下和齊利科先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著昨天寫的信這是近況報告第四彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從葛拉學園逃出來的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安無事地將妲妮亞同學送到了她父母那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說葛拉學園的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暫且住在了妲妮亞同學的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們都說終有一日會去他們各自該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們又再次奔向荒野了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上了尋找在葛拉村莊突然不見了的疤面小姐的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們指路的是瑟莉卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在歐塔斯瑟莉卡小姐將疤面小姐呼喚到了自己身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次一定也會找到疤面小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說已經事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋疤面這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是為了她好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底她是守墓人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂守墓人就是追尋著死者的氣息單獨進行旅行的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話疤面不也只是回歸了她本應有的樣子而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這個是有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听疤面親口對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說我想見疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要就這樣...見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣我都應該多幫助一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在葛拉艾不見了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面開始變得十分不鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對瑟莉卡之前還是一直緊緊地抱著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間就丟下不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又突然害怕得顫抖起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道她這樣不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼事情都沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好萬無一失的是西北加3度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見疤面小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼之前不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊又沒問我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日這種事不慶祝是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是蒂伊同學想起來的話就糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是艾利斯同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔有什麼要幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話還沒有說完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說沒事了還有什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但但這是生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要說生日快樂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一年一度的很重要的節日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在不是乾這種事情的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個我可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日算個什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵你給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把那些東西捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日就該大家一起慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯同學多大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十...六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯同學祝你16歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起慶祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生你會做蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才是關鍵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快把蠟燭吹滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要好好許願哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡不行吧餵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛那這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說那裡更不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到大叔會這麼適合當父親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經...是位父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生失去了他的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是人類或守墓人都是會變的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真是複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像的要更加的更加的複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然挺有趣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也到處旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從未見過像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是貶義哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵這不能算是回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來路就很難走還是這樣的能見度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇好壯觀的霧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是壯觀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得是不好的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說別抱怨了快點趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡...是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先暫時回車上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這霧裡走散了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的是雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是STORY CIRCLE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是守墓人們出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是同樣的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂守墓人就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少則幾百人多則會有上千人一模一樣的個體被確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如「貝傑爾家族」「蒂紐家族」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究者們會將同一類型的守墓人命名後分類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有許多只被確認過一次的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈娜小姐肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是來到了一個鳥不拉屎的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面小姐是想回到自己出生的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧的好厲害是迄今為止反應最大的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟莉卡難道疤面就在這附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這前方「守墓人出生的地方」將會一直持續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂伊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只感覺到不好的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經一起來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不知道嗎我是個很容易反复無常的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂伊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那副表情算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了能見度越來越低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們已經很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之慢慢前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟莉卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親父親將母親寶貴的夢想給...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經...完全搞不懂了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是媽媽的夢想是媽媽的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓你活下去的唯一的一句話就是「想活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是出生在這裡的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個如果疤面小姐想像以前一樣作為守墓人活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能強行地去阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟莉卡要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣和瑟莉卡分別真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別將那孩子靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那孩子還在我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為守墓人為活人們能夠有美好人生而...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓人是不會哭泣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我們的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾真是軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...蒂伊同學不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日曆還停留在14年前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不到任何死人的氣死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是拯救世界
